## 9. Module-wise Description

### 9.1 Authentication & Security Module

**Files**: [SecurityConfig.java](file:///c:/Users/Shuddhodhan/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/PlasticWasteTracker/src/main/java/com/plasticaudit/config/SecurityConfig.java), [AuthController.java](file:///c:/Users/Shuddhodhan/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/PlasticWasteTracker/src/main/java/com/plasticaudit/controller/AuthController.java), [CustomAuthenticationSuccessHandler.java](file:///c:/Users/Shuddhodhan/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/PlasticWasteTracker/src/main/java/com/plasticaudit/config/CustomAuthenticationSuccessHandler.java)

Spring Security 6 secures all routes. A custom `AuthenticationSuccessHandler` performs post-login role detection and redirects users to the appropriate dashboard view.

**URL Authorization Matrix:**

| URL Pattern | Allowed Roles |
|-------------|--------------|
| `/login`, `/css/**`, `/js/**` | PUBLIC |
| `/admin/**` | ROLE_ADMIN only |
| `/waste/**`, `/reports/**` | ROLE_ADMIN, ROLE_INDUSTRY |
| `/prediction/**` | ROLE_ADMIN, ROLE_INDUSTRY |
| `/dashboard/**` | ROLE_ADMIN, ROLE_INDUSTRY |
| `/**` | Authenticated |

**Security Configuration Chain:**
```mermaid
flowchart LR
    A[HTTP Request] --> B[CSRF Filter]
    B --> C[RequestLoggingFilter]
    C --> D[UsernamePasswordAuthFilter]
    D --> E{Authenticated?}
    E -- No --> F[Redirect /login]
    E -- Yes --> G{Authorized?}
    G -- No --> H[403 Access Denied]
    G -- Yes --> I[Controller Method]
```

**Password Encoding**: BCrypt with strength 12 (`BCryptPasswordEncoder`).

**Session Management**: Stateful session with `maximumSessions(1)` to prevent duplicate concurrent logins.

---

### 9.2 Dashboard Module

**Files**: [DashboardController.java](file:///c:/Users/Shuddhodhan/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/PlasticWasteTracker/src/main/java/com/plasticaudit/controller/DashboardController.java), [templates/dashboard/index.html](file:///c:/Users/Shuddhodhan/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/PlasticWasteTracker/src/main/resources/templates/dashboard/index.html)

The dashboard adapts dynamically based on the authenticated user's role:

**Admin (Regulator) View:**
- Global SDG metrics: Total Generated, Recycled, Eliminated across all industries
- Overall Reduction Rate and Recycling Ratio
- List of all registered industries with targets
- AI Prediction & Risk widget section

**Industry User View:**
- Own waste entry history (most recent 10)
- SDG metrics scoped to their industry only
- Per-entry Reduction Rate badges
- AI Prediction shortcut card

**SDG Metric Calculation Flow:**
```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Browser
    participant DashboardController
    participant WasteEntryRepository
    participant MySQL

    Browser->>DashboardController: GET /dashboard
    DashboardController->>WasteEntryRepository: getGlobalSdgMetrics()
    WasteEntryRepository->>MySQL: SELECT SUM(generated), SUM(recycled), SUM(eliminated)
    MySQL-->>WasteEntryRepository: [totals]
    WasteEntryRepository-->>DashboardController: Object[]
    DashboardController->>DashboardController: calculate reductionRate & recyclingRatio
    DashboardController-->>Browser: Model with sdgGenerated, sdgRecycled, sdgEliminated, sdgReductionRate, sdgRecyclingRatio
```

---

### 9.3 Waste Entry Module

**Files**: [WasteEntryController.java](file:///c:/Users/Shuddhodhan/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/PlasticWasteTracker/src/main/java/com/plasticaudit/controller/WasteEntryController.java), [WasteEntryService.java](file:///c:/Users/Shuddhodhan/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/PlasticWasteTracker/src/main/java/com/plasticaudit/service/WasteEntryService.java), [WasteEntryRepository.java](file:///c:/Users/Shuddhodhan/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/PlasticWasteTracker/src/main/java/com/plasticaudit/repository/WasteEntryRepository.java), [BatchWasteJdbcRepository.java](file:///c:/Users/Shuddhodhan/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/PlasticWasteTracker/src/main/java/com/plasticaudit/jdbc/BatchWasteJdbcRepository.java)

Core data-entry module. Industry users log monthly plastic data here.

**WasteEntry Lifecycle:**
```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Draft: User fills form
    Draft --> Submitted: POST /waste/save
    Submitted --> Validated: Service validates recycled <= generated
    Validated --> Persisted: JPA save()
    Persisted --> Verified: Admin marks verified=true
    Verified --> Aggregated: Included in AuditReport
    Aggregated --> [*]
```

**CRUD Operations:**
| Method | URL | Description |
|--------|-----|-------------|
| GET | `/waste/list` | List all entries (admin) or own entries (industry user) |
| GET | `/waste/new` | Show blank entry form |
| POST | `/waste/save` | Persist new entry |
| GET | `/waste/delete/{id}` | Delete entry (admin only) |

**Batch Import (JDBC)**: [BatchWasteJdbcRepository](file:///c:/Users/Shuddhodhan/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/PlasticWasteTracker/src/main/java/com/plasticaudit/jdbc/BatchWasteJdbcRepository.java#18-115) uses raw `PreparedStatement.addBatch()` for bulk import operations (e.g., CSV upload). Executes every 50 rows for memory efficiency. Full transaction with manual `conn.setAutoCommit(false)` / `rollback()` on error.

---

### 9.4 Report & Audit Module

**Files**: [ReportController.java](file:///c:/Users/Shuddhodhan/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/PlasticWasteTracker/src/main/java/com/plasticaudit/controller/ReportController.java), [ReportAggregatorService.java](file:///c:/Users/Shuddhodhan/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/PlasticWasteTracker/src/main/java/com/plasticaudit/service/ReportAggregatorService.java), [AuditReportRepository.java](file:///c:/Users/Shuddhodhan/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/PlasticWasteTracker/src/main/java/com/plasticaudit/repository/AuditReportRepository.java)

Audit reports aggregate all waste entries for a given period per industry, compute compliance metrics, and persist the result.

**Report Generation Flow (Async):**
```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Admin
    participant ReportController
    participant ReportAggregatorService
    participant WasteEntryRepository
    participant AuditReportRepository

    Admin->>ReportController: POST /reports/generate (periodStart, periodEnd)
    ReportController->>ReportAggregatorService: aggregateReportsForAllIndustries() @Async
    ReportController-->>Admin: redirect /reports (immediately, before reports done)
    loop For each Industry
        ReportAggregatorService->>WasteEntryRepository: sumGenerated/Recycled/Eliminated
        WasteEntryRepository-->>ReportAggregatorService: totals
        ReportAggregatorService->>ReportAggregatorService: calculate rates + compliance
        ReportAggregatorService->>AuditReportRepository: save(AuditReport)
    end
    ReportAggregatorService-->>ReportController: CompletableFuture<List<AuditReport>>
```

**AuditReport Status Lifecycle:**
```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> DRAFT: Generated by system
    DRAFT --> APPROVED: Admin approves
    DRAFT --> REJECTED: Admin rejects
    APPROVED --> [*]
    REJECTED --> DRAFT: Re-generate
```

**Compliance Logic:**
- `complianceStatus = PASS` if `reductionRatePercent >= 30`
- `complianceStatus = FAIL` if below 30%
- Stored in `remarks` field of AuditReport

