### 9.5 AI Prediction & Analytics Module

**Files**: [PredictionService.java](file:///c:/Users/Shuddhodhan/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/PlasticWasteTracker/src/main/java/com/plasticaudit/prediction/PredictionService.java), [PredictionController.java](file:///c:/Users/Shuddhodhan/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/PlasticWasteTracker/src/main/java/com/plasticaudit/prediction/PredictionController.java), [PredictionResult.java](file:///c:/Users/Shuddhodhan/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/PlasticWasteTracker/src/main/java/com/plasticaudit/prediction/PredictionResult.java), [WasteDataPoint.java](file:///c:/Users/Shuddhodhan/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/PlasticWasteTracker/src/main/java/com/plasticaudit/prediction/WasteDataPoint.java)  
**Templates**: [prediction/index.html](file:///c:/Users/Shuddhodhan/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/PlasticWasteTracker/src/main/resources/templates/prediction/index.html), [prediction/select.html](file:///c:/Users/Shuddhodhan/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/PlasticWasteTracker/src/main/resources/templates/prediction/select.html)

This module transforms the tracker into an intelligent decision-support system. Implemented without external ML libraries using **Ordinary Least Squares (OLS) Simple Linear Regression** in pure Java.

**Data Flow:**
```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[WasteEntry rows from DB] --> B[Aggregate by YearMonth]
    B --> C[WasteDataPoint list sorted chronologically]
    C --> D{count >= 3?}
    D -- No --> E[Return insufficient data message]
    D -- Yes --> F[OLS Linear Regression on generated, recycled, eliminated]
    F --> G[Predict next month values]
    G --> H[Compute: growth rate, recycling trend, averages]
    H --> I[Assess Risk Level - LOW/MEDIUM/HIGH]
    I --> J[Generate contextual Recommendations]
    J --> K[Serialize chart data to JSON]
    K --> L[Return PredictionResult to Controller]
    L --> M[Render prediction/index.html with Chart.js]
```

**Algorithm detail** — see Section 16.

