## 11. Sequence Diagrams

### 11.1 User Login Sequence

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Browser
    participant Spring Security
    participant UserDetailsService
    participant MySQL

    User->>Browser: Enter username + password + role
    Browser->>Spring Security: POST /login
    Spring Security->>UserDetailsService: loadUserByUsername(username)
    UserDetailsService->>MySQL: SELECT user JOIN roles WHERE username=?
    MySQL-->>UserDetailsService: User entity + roles
    UserDetailsService-->>Spring Security: UserDetails
    Spring Security->>Spring Security: BCrypt.matches(rawPassword, encoded)
    alt Correct credentials
        Spring Security->>CustomAuthSuccessHandler: onAuthenticationSuccess()
        CustomAuthSuccessHandler->>Browser: redirect /dashboard
    else Wrong credentials
        Spring Security->>Browser: redirect /login?error
    end
```

### 11.2 Waste Entry Submission Sequence

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Industry User
    participant WasteEntryController
    participant WasteEntryService
    participant AlertServer
    participant MySQL

    Industry User->>WasteEntryController: POST /waste/save (form data)
    WasteEntryController->>WasteEntryController: Validate industryId ownership
    WasteEntryController->>WasteEntryService: save(entry)
    WasteEntryService->>WasteEntryService: Validate recycled <= generated
    WasteEntryService->>WasteEntryService: Validate eliminated <= generated
    WasteEntryService->>MySQL: INSERT waste_entries
    MySQL-->>WasteEntryService: saved entry
    WasteEntryService->>AlertServer: broadcastAlert("New entry logged")
    AlertServer->>AlertServer: Notify all connected regulators
    WasteEntryController-->>Industry User: redirect /waste/list (successMsg)
```

### 11.3 AI Prediction Sequence

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant PredictionController
    participant PredictionService
    participant WasteEntryRepository
    participant MySQL

    User->>PredictionController: GET /prediction/{industryId}
    PredictionController->>PredictionController: Check ownership/role
    PredictionController->>PredictionService: predictNextMonthWaste(industryId)
    PredictionService->>WasteEntryRepository: findByIndustryId(id)
    WasteEntryRepository->>MySQL: SELECT ... JOIN FETCH industry WHERE industry_id=?
    MySQL-->>WasteEntryRepository: List<WasteEntry>
    WasteEntryRepository-->>PredictionService: entries
    PredictionService->>PredictionService: Aggregate by YearMonth -> List<WasteDataPoint>
    PredictionService->>PredictionService: OLS Linear Regression on generated, recycled, eliminated
    PredictionService->>PredictionService: Compute trends, growth rate, recycling trend
    PredictionService->>PredictionService: Assess risk level (LOW/MEDIUM/HIGH)
    PredictionService->>PredictionService: Generate contextual recommendations
    PredictionService-->>PredictionController: PredictionResult
    PredictionController->>PredictionController: Serialize chart data to JSON
    PredictionController-->>User: Render prediction/index.html + Chart.js
```

