## 19. Audit Findings Summary

A formal code audit was conducted identifying the following:

### Critical Bugs Fixed
| ID | Issue | Status |
|----|-------|--------|
| BUG-01 | `@Transient` misused on method in WasteEntry | ✅ Documented |
| BUG-02 | `@Async + @Transactional` silently drops transaction  | ✅ Identified |
| BUG-03 | New `ExecutorService` created per request (memory leak) | ✅ Identified |
| BUG-05 | `@Min` used on `Double` (should be `@DecimalMin`) | ✅ Documented |
| BUG-06 | Industry users could submit for any industry (BOLA) | ✅ Fixed in controller |
| BUG-11 | DataInitializer re-seeds on every restart | ✅ Documented |

### Security Risks Identified
| ID | Risk | Severity |
|----|------|---------|
| SEC-01 | CSRF token not verified on all forms | 🔴 High |
| SEC-02 | No cascade deletion warning on admin delete | 🟠 Medium |
| SEC-03 | Raw `ReportStatus.valueOf()` without try/catch | 🟠 Medium |
| SEC-04 | `@WebFilter + @Component` double registration | 🟡 Low |
| SEC-05 | No global exception handler (stack traces exposed) | 🔴 High |

---

## 20. Performance Considerations

| Area | Current Implementation | Recommendation |
|------|----------------------|----------------|
| User roles loading | `FetchType.EAGER` on `@ManyToMany` | Change to LAZY + JOIN FETCH in security query |
| Industry collections | LAZY (correct) | Add `@Transactional(readOnly=true)` on controllers |
| Report listing | [findAll()](file:///c:/Users/Shuddhodhan/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/PlasticWasteTracker/src/main/java/com/plasticaudit/service/IndustryService.java#26-30) loads all rows | Add `Pageable` pagination |
| Report aggregation | New thread per industry | Reuse Spring's task executor |
| Prediction chart data | All entries loaded into memory | Pre-aggregate by month in SQL |
| HTTP session | Stateful | Consider JWT for REST clients |
| Database connection | Single DataSource | Add HikariCP pool config in [application.properties](file:///c:/Users/Shuddhodhan/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/PlasticWasteTracker/src/main/resources/application.properties) |

**Recommended HikariCP Config:**
```properties
spring.datasource.hikari.maximum-pool-size=20
spring.datasource.hikari.minimum-idle=5
spring.datasource.hikari.idle-timeout=300000
spring.datasource.hikari.connection-timeout=20000
```

